'''馬克·丹尼爾·朗森'''（{{lang-en|Mark Daniel Ronson}}，{{bd|1975年|9月4日}}）是一位兼擁英美籍的[[音樂家|音樂家]]、[[唱片騎師|DJ]]、[[歌手|詞曲作家]]及[[音樂製作人|音樂製作人]]。

儘管他的首張專輯《{{le|名人操盤手|Here Comes the Fuzz}}》未能衝擊排行榜，但他的第二張專輯《{{le|譯想天開|Version (album)}}》仍登上[[英國專輯排行榜|英國專輯排行榜]]亞軍，且包含了3首英國十強單曲。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.officialcharts.com/artist/_/mark%20ronson/|title=UK Charts - Mark Ronson|publisher=Official Charts Company|accessdate=2014-12-26|archive-date=2014-12-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141222030911/http://www.officialcharts.com/artist/_/Mark%20Ronson|dead-url=no}}</ref>這也使他在2008年贏得[[全英音樂獎|全英音樂獎]]最佳英國男歌手。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.brits.co.uk/artist/mark-ronson |title=Mark Ronson |publisher=Brits.co.uk |date=2014-02-19 |accessdate=2014-07-16 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141006093511/http://www.brits.co.uk/artist/mark-ronson |archivedate=2014-10-06 }}</ref>他在2010年9月27日發行第三張錄音室專輯《{{le|唱片大玩家|Record Collection (album)}}》。朗森在2014年以與[[火星人布魯諾|火星人布魯諾]]合作的單曲〈[[放克名流|放克名流]]〉首次奪得英國金榜冠軍。<ref name=":1">{{cite web|url=http://www.officialcharts.com/chart-news/uptown-funk-gives-mark-ronson-his-first-number-1-single-3353/|title=Uptown Funk gives Mark Ronson his first Number 1 single|first=Rob|last=Copsey|publisher=Official Charts Company|date=2014-12-14|accessdate=2014-12-14|archive-date=2014-12-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141214215953/https://www.officialcharts.com/chart-news/uptown-funk-gives-mark-ronson-his-first-number-1-single-3353/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

他也曾為[[艾美·懷恩豪斯|艾美·懷恩豪斯]]及[[愛黛兒|愛黛兒]]製作[[葛萊美獎|葛萊美獎]]獲獎專輯。

== 早年生活 ==
朗森生於[[聖約翰伍德|聖約翰伍德]]的[[惠靈頓醫院|惠靈頓醫院]]（Wellington Hospital），母親為社交名媛安·德克斯特-瓊斯（Ann Dexter-Jones），父親為地產大亨及音樂經紀人勞倫斯·朗森（Laurence Ronson）。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.harpersbazaar.com/celebrity/red-carpet-dresses/the-royal-ronsons-0908|title=Mark, Charlotte, and Samantha Ronson, Ann Dexter-Jones, The Royal Tenenbaums|work=Harper's BAZAAR Magazine|publisher=Hearst Communications|first=Sarah|last=Cristobal|date=2008-08-10|accessdate=2015-01-08|archive-date=2015-01-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150117211622/https://www.harpersbazaar.com/celebrity/red-carpet-dresses/a327/the-royal-ronsons-0908/|dead-url=no}}</ref>他的雙親皆是[[阿什肯納茲猶太人|阿什肯納茲猶太人]]（他的祖先是來自奧地利、俄羅斯與立陶宛的猶太移民）；朗森生長於[[猶太教保守派|猶太教保守派]]家庭，後來受猶太成年禮。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.guiltandpleasure.com/index.php?site=rebootgp&page=gp_article&id=76 |title=Guilt & Pleasure |publisher=Guiltandpleasure.com |date=2007-09-26 |accessdate=2014-07-16 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131210023928/http://www.guiltandpleasure.com/index.php?site=rebootgp&page=gp_article&id=76 |archivedate=2013-12-10 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.dailyjews.com/articles/693_mark_ronson_intervie.htm |title=Mark Ronson interview |publisher=DailyJews |date=2007-07-03 |accessdate=2014-07-16 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110716065820/http://www.dailyjews.com/articles/693_mark_ronson_intervie.htm |archivedate=2011-07-16 }}</ref>朗森的姓氏本來是阿朗森（Aaronson），但他的祖父亨利·朗森（Henry Ronson）將之改為朗森。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-509291/The-truth-svengali-seen-paying-late-night-visit-troubled-Amy-Winehouses-hotel.html|work=Daily Mail|location=UK|title=The truth about the svengali seen paying a late-night visit to troubled Amy Winehouse's hotel|first=Claudia|last=Joseph|date=2008-01-20|accessdate=2011-01-11|archive-date=2016-12-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161231000511/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-509291/The-truth-svengali-seen-paying-late-night-visit-troubled-Amy-Winehouses-hotel.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>他是地產大亨{{le|杰拉德·朗森|Gerald Ronson}}的姪子。而他因為母親的緣故，與英國[[保守黨_(英國)|保守黨]]政治家[[馬爾科姆·里夫金德|馬爾科姆·里夫金德]]與{{le|里昂·布里坦|Leon Brittan}}，<ref name="entertainment.timesonline.co.uk">{{cite news|url=http://entertainment.timesonline.co.uk/tol/arts_and_entertainment/music/article3257098.ece|work=The Times|location=London|title=The man Amy and Lily go to when they want a hit|date=2008-01-28|accessdate=2010-05-12|archive-date=2008-05-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080511172748/http://entertainment.timesonline.co.uk/tol/arts_and_entertainment/music/article3257098.ece|dead-url=no}}</ref>以及{{le|歐點電影院|Odeon Cinemas}}創辦人{{le|奧斯卡·德意志|Oscar Deutsch}}有血緣關係。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/lifeandstyle/2010/jun/26/rock-pop-dexter-jones-sansom|location=London|work=The Guardian|title=Great dynasties of the world: The Dexter-Joneses|first=Ian|last=Sansom|date=2010-06-26|accessdate=2015-01-08|archive-date=2010-07-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100702032152/http://www.guardian.co.uk/lifeandstyle/2010/jun/26/rock-pop-dexter-jones-sansom|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/3667186/Mark-Ronson-The-Forrest-Gump-of-hip-hop.html|title=Mark Ronson: The Forrest Gump of hip-hop?|first=Ravi|last=Somaiya|date=2007-08-12|work=The Telegraph|publisher=Telegraph Media Group|accessdate=2015-01-08|archive-date=2020-11-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201121060122/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/3667186/Mark-Ronson-The-Forrest-Gump-of-hip-hop.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

朗森有一對比他小兩歲的雙胞胎妹妹，時尚設計師{{le|夏綠蒂·朗森|Charlotte Ronson}}與歌手兼唱片騎師的{{le|薩曼莎·朗森|Samantha Ronson}}。朗森還有五位同父異母及同母異父的兄弟姊妹。亞歷山大（Alexander）和安娜貝爾（Annabelle）是他母親與米克·瓊斯再婚的小孩，以及亨麗埃塔（Henrietta）、大衛（David）和約書亞（Joshua）是他父親與模特兒米歇爾·弗斯特（Michele First）再婚的小孩。在他雙親分手後，他的母親與{{le|外國人合唱團|Foreigner (band)}}的吉他手{{le|米克·瓊斯|Mick Jones (Foreigner)}}結婚，這促成了他從小的音樂素養。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://music.guardian.co.uk/pop/alexispetridis/story/0,,2183270,00.html|work=The Guardian|location=London|title=Cover boy|first=Alexis|last=Petridis|date=2007-10-06|accessdate=2010-05-12|archive-date=2008-04-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080420172206/http://music.guardian.co.uk/pop/alexispetridis/story/0,,2183270,00.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>馬克·朗森是[[約翰·藍儂|約翰·藍儂]]與[[小野洋子|小野洋子]]之子[[西恩·藍儂|西恩·藍儂]]的兒時玩伴。<ref>{{cite web |last=Byrne |first=Suzy |url=https://music.yahoo.com/blogs/yahoo-music/foreigners-mick-jones-reminisces-about-opening-for-the-beatles-215215320.html |title=Foreigner's Mick Jones Reminisces About Opening for the Beatles |publisher=Music.yahoo.com |date=2014-02-07 |accessdate=2014-07-16 |archive-date=2014-10-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141006153138/https://music.yahoo.com/blogs/yahoo-music/foreigners-mick-jones-reminisces-about-opening-for-the-beatles-215215320.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

==個人生活==
朗森大部分的時間都待在倫敦及紐約。他的繼父是{{le|外國人合唱團|Foreigner (band)}}的{{le|米克·瓊斯|Mick Jones (Foreigner)}}，他從朗森七歲時開始撫養他。<ref>{{cite web |author= |url=http://www.songfacts.com/blog/interviews/mick_jones_of_foreigner/ |title=Mick Jones of Foreigner: Songwriter Interviews |publisher=Songfacts.com |date=2009-10-23 |accessdate=2014-07-16 |archive-date=2018-07-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180724122808/http://www.songfacts.com/blog/interviews/mick_jones_of_foreigner/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

他於2002年開始與[[昆西·瓊斯|昆西·瓊斯]]的女兒，演員及女歌手{{le|拉西達·瓊斯|Rashida Jones}}約會。<ref>(13 May 2002), "rashida jones". ''People''. '''57''' (18):140</ref>雙方在2003年3月訂婚，朗森設計了一個有「妳願意嫁給我嗎」（Will you marry me）信息的填字遊戲向她求婚。<ref>Abel, Olivia (17 March 2003), "Passages". ''People''. '''59''' (10):81</ref>他們的關係在大約一年後結束<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.tvguide.com/celebrities/rashida-jones/bio/193824|title=Rashida Jones: Biography|publisher=''TV Guide''|accessdate=2008-10-02|archive-date=2008-10-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081026025415/http://www.tvguide.com/celebrities/rashida-jones/bio/193824|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.people.com/people/archive/article/0,,20139544,00.html|title=Passages|last=Abel|first=Olivia|date=2003-03-17|publisher=''People''|accessdate=2009-07-01|archive-date=2017-08-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170813145405/http://people.com/archive/passages-vol-59-no-10/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

朗森之後在2011年2月與曾出現在〈The Bike Song〉音樂錄影帶中的法國演員及歌手{{le|約瑟芬·德·拉·波美|Joséphine de La Baume}}訂婚。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-1355585/Mark-Ronson-gets-engaged-Josephine-De-La-Baume.html|title=Mark Ronson gets engaged to his Agent Provocateur model and actress girlfriend Josephine de La Baume|work=Daily Mail|date=2011-02-10|accessdate=2011-02-10|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304125354/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-1355585/Mark-Ronson-gets-engaged-Josephine-De-La-Baume.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>他們於2011年9月5日在法國南部的[[普羅旺斯地區艾克斯|普羅旺斯地區艾克斯]]結婚。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/celebritynews/8739722/Mark-Ronson-marries-Josephine-de-la-Baume-in-Provence.html|title=Mark Ronson marries Josephine de la Baume in Provence|work=The Telegraph|date=2011-09-03|accessdate=2015-01-15|archive-date=2020-11-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201128025424/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/celebritynews/8739722/Mark-Ronson-marries-Josephine-de-la-Baume-in-Provence.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-2033256/Mark-Ronson-marries-French-bride-Josephine-la-Baume-Provence.html|title=And the groom wore candy stripes! Mark Ronson marries his French bride Josephine de la Baume in romantic Provence|work=Daily Mail|date=2011-09-05|accessdate=2015-01-15|archive-date=2020-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112020853/https://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-2033256/Mark-Ronson-marries-French-bride-Josephine-la-Baume-Provence.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>這段關係於2018年10月結束。

於2021年6月宣布與演員[[梅麗·史翠普|梅麗·史翠普]]二女兒，同樣身為演員的{{le|葛瑞絲‧古墨|Grace_Gummer}}結婚。<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.usmagazine.com/celebrity-news/news/grace-gummer-mark-ronson-engaged/ |title=Meryl Streep’s Daughter Grace Gummer Is Engaged to Mark Ronson |date=2021-06-10 |accessdate=2021-06-10 |archive-date=2022-02-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220217151144/https://www.usmagazine.com/celebrity-news/news/grace-gummer-mark-ronson-engaged/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

